<i>verb</i>: 멈추다 [멈추다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>멈추다 [멈추다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stop; halt</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 비 등이 그만 내리다.</dd><br>
<dd>For snow, rain, etc., to stop falling.</dd><br>
<dd>2. stop doing; quit</dd><br>
<dd>동작이나 상태가 계속되지 않다.</dd><br>
<dd>For a gesture or state not to continue.</dd><br>
<dd>3. stay still; unmoving</dd><br>
<dd>계속 움직이지 않다.</dd><br>
<dd>To stay without any movement.</dd><br>
<dd>4. stop; quit</dd><br>
<dd>하던 일이나 동작을 그만 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To stop a task or action that one has been engaged in.</dd><br>
<dd>5. stop someone</dd><br>
<dd>하던 일이나 동작을 그만 하게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make one stop a task or action that one has been engaged in.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>